                        </h3>
                        <div class="detail-item">
                            <span class="detail-label">Booking ID:</span>
                            <span class="detail-value">
                                <span class="queue-id-badge" id="queueId">Loading...</span>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="detail-item">
                            <span class="detail-label">Date:</span>
                            <span class="detail-value" id="appointmentDate">Loading...</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="detail-item">
                            <span class="detail-label">Time:</span>
                            <span class="detail-value" id="appointmentTime">Loading...</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="detail-item">
                            <span class="detail-label">Treatment:</span>
                            <span class="detail-value" id="treatmentName">Loading...</span>
